dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.sender_name: Guru Denim Inc, DBA True Religion Brand Jeans
dmca.principal_name: Guru Denim Inc, DBA True Religion Brand Jeans

works.description:
The copyrighted infringement at issue is the use of copyrighted images and text without authorization from the IP Owner.
Website displays IP Owner’s copyrighted waist patches and labels and displays IP Owner’s copyrighted promotional photos of jeans and other products as used by IP Owner’s official website, www.truereligionbrandjeans.com.
Please Note: Most images used by the counterfeit websites are from past seasons, and may not be currently available on our website.
